text: William Rozier (1908 - 15 January 1983) was a French swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1983 deaths Category:French male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of France Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
